The API docs point to the latest stable release. Fixes to the API docs are reflected the next time that docset is published, or for the default one, whenever the stable version switches.
To change this, we'd have to backport the fix to 1.1, and redeploy the 1.1 docs.
@wolffg FYI -- I know of no plans to redeploy old docs regularly.

